videos.description: In the second quarter of the WNBA All-Star game, Elena Delle Donne finds A'ja Wilson for two buckets and chants MVP.

videos.description: Maya Moore's 18-point performance earns MVP honors as Team Parker beats Team Delle Donne 119-112 in the 2018 WNBA All-Star Game.
